This is just a git version of Ubuntu's audio_test script from checkbox.

This mirrors the authoritative source location which is at:

https://code.launchpad.net/~roadmr/+junk/audio_test

This script requires Python 3.0 with gi, gstreamer and pulseaudio.
It should work out of the box on Ubuntu 13.04 and higher.

1- If you're running Ubuntu 12.04, add a PPA containing GStreamer 1.0:

sudo apt-add-repository ppa:gstreamer-developers/ppa

2- If on Ubuntu 12.04, install the following packages:
 python3
 python3-gi
 gir1.2-gstreamer-1.0
 libgstreamer1.0-0
 gstreamer1.0-plugins-good
 gstreamer1.0-pulseaudio

3- run ./audio_test

